OL,3,CJohn Swinney to visit Kentucky for
OL,4,Cwhisky talks during US visit
OL,6,FScotland's First Minister will visit
OL,7,FKentucky during his trip to America.
OL,9,FJohn Swinney flew to Boston last week
OL,10,Fto watch the nation's first World Cup
OL,11,Fmatch for 28 years, where Scotland
OL,12,Fbeat Haiti 1-0.
OL,14,FThe SNP leader will now head to the
OL,15,Fstate of Kentucky where he will meet
OL,16,Fbourbon business leaders.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/5
