OL,3,CJohn Swinney to visit Kentucky for
OL,4,Cwhisky talks during US visit
OL,6,FThe Scottish Government said the First
OL,7,FMinister aims to "keep up the
OL,8,Fmomentum" for Scotch after US
OL,9,FPresident Donald Trump's commitment to
OL,10,Fremove the 10% tariff on whisky.
OL,12,FDuring his trip, he will co-host a
OL,13,Flunch with American bourbon leaders,
OL,14,Fvisit Kentucky Cooperage and Kentucky
OL,15,FBourbon Barrel, and tour a distillery
OL,16,Fwith members of the Congressional
OL,17,FBourbon Caucus.
OL,26,@oD@ROUpD@IO]
