OL,3,CJohn Swinney to visit Kentucky for
OL,4,Cwhisky talks during US visit
OL,6,FMr Trump announced in May that he
OL,7,Fwould remove the 10% tariff on whisky.
OL,8,FThe move is a big win for Scotland's
OL,9,Fnational drink, with the American
OL,10,Fmarket, its biggest, worth nearly #1
OL,11,Fbillion.
OL,13,FWhisky exports to the US fell by 4% in
OL,14,Fvalue and more than 9% in volume
OL,15,Fcompared with 2024, which the Scottish
OL,16,FGovernment said made "the removal of
OL,17,Ftrade barriers such as tariffs a high
OL,18,Fpriority".
OL,26,@xD@VOUzD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/5
