OL,3,CJohn Swinney to visit Kentucky for
OL,4,Cwhisky talks during US visit
OL,6,FMr Swinney said: "Scotch whisky and
OL,7,FKentucky bourbon share a deep, long-
OL,8,Fstanding connection ` they're two of
OL,9,Fthe world's great spirits and of high
OL,10,Fvalue to their respective economies.
OL,12,F"Every year, millions of used bourbon
OL,13,Fbarrels make their way from Kentucky
OL,14,Fto Scotland, where they're used to age
OL,15,Fsome of the world's finest Scotch
OL,16,Fwhiskies.
OL,18,F"The relationship between these two
OL,19,Fgreat spirits industries is genuinely
OL,20,Fsymbiotic ` each one helps make the
OL,21,Fother better.
OL,26,@nD@ROUtD@AOUzD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1781482667
OL,3,CJohn Swinney to visit Kentucky for
OL,4,Cwhisky talks during US visit
OL,6,F"I have consistently made the case to
OL,7,Fexempt Scotch whisky from the 10%
OL,8,Ftariff and was pleased by the
OL,9,Fpresident's announcement that he would
OL,10,Fremove the tariff for whisky following
OL,11,Fthe state visit earlier this year.
OL,13,F"My visit to Kentucky aims to build on
OL,14,Fboth that shared heritage and
OL,15,FPresident Trump's commitment to remove
OL,16,Fthe tariff for whisky, in a very
OL,17,Fimportant overseas market for Scotch."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUyD@fO]
